rows.label: tlk70000076_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Are you lot going to do
something about all this?

rows.label: tlk70000076_05_msg0002
rows.name:
My squad's been recalled. The
situation's looking very serious.

rows.label: tlk70000076_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I mean... I'm a soldier, of course...
but before that I'm a human being.
A sentient being, that is...

rows.label: tlk70000076_05_msg0004
rows.name:
If others are in need, does it really
matter where they come from? Gulan,
Superbian... We're all people.

rows.label: tlk70000076_05_msg0005
rows.name:
I want to do everything I can to
help with the relief and the
evacutation, right up to the end.

rows.label: tlk70000076_05_msg0006
rows.name:
It pains me to say it, but
implore you to do here
what the Empire cannot.
